        p
          | Cards can be used for creating layouts for image albums, blog posts, ecommerce products etc. Big companies like Google and Facebook are making use of cards for their different web platforms.
        p
          | Normally, if we want to create complex layouts based on cards, we&apos;d need to have deep knowledge of CSS and HTML. However, thanks to the latest features of Bootstrap, we can quickly build such layouts by wrapping our set of cards inside 
          code div
          | s with some special classes such as
          code .card-group
          | , 
          code .card-deck
          |  and 
          code .card-columns
          | .
